-- RadioShack CEO steps down
-- 
-- Wed Sep 26, 2012 7:38am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/09/26/us-radioshack-ceo-idUSBRE88P0NS20120926

 

 (Reuters) - U.S. consumer electronics chain RadioShack Corp ( RSH.N ) said Chief Executive James Gooch will step down from his position, effective immediately. 
 The company's said its board is conducting a search for a successor and would not rule out internal candidates. Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer Dorvin Lively will be the acting CEO. (Reporting by Juhi Arora in Bangalore; Editing by Joyjeet Das)